title: Way Out West S01E01 Welcome To The Backcountry WEB-DL x264-RKSTR
description:
Follow the Youren, Bullock and Korell families as they compete to lead the best excursions, survive their various family shenanigans and participate in local festivals and time-honored traditions.

Way.Out.West.S01E01.Welcome.To.The.Backcountry.WEB-DL.x264-RKSTR

The Korells, the Bullocks, and the Yourens try to settle once and for all which family is the best at outfitting. But rather than challenge each other to real hunting and camping events, they come up with a crazy collection of challenges... including a madcap horse drawn chariot race! And when more clients than expected show up, the Korells have to take drastic measures to keep their guests happy.
